{"id": 1933, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都收到过哪些无用的职场教导？", "description": "仔细琢磨一下，你觉得哪些“职场前辈”给年轻人的建议其实是陈词滥调？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2090, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170928151139qXafu3F0PRsWng1K.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-29T03:00:57Z", "options": [{"id": 239104, "content": "告诉新人如何才能涨薪，试过才知道全TM是假的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106416}, {"id": 238871, "content": "“有点眼色，搞好关系。”但是说这些话的人往往并不是最吃得开的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 287, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570398}, {"id": 238872, "content": "“不要给上级送东西”", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672002}, {"id": 238873, "content": "既来之则安之、要学会做人、要和群、你这就是不懂政治了、你知道XX是XX的人嘛、现在的年轻人啊~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893313}, {"id": 239130, "content": "领导喜欢说 “我们这么做都是为你好”可事实是明明让我很为难", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144528}, {"id": 238876, "content": "学一门技能…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903090}, {"id": 238877, "content": "最烦的就是各类成功学，比如马云刘强东啥的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607970}, {"id": 239133, "content": "年轻人一定要学一项赚钱的技能，找个稳定的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903090}, {"id": 238878, "content": "最后根本不知道学什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903090}, {"id": 238879, "content": "狼性文化。那种薪资水平不到别人一半提出和别人大公司一样的要求还说是高要求，对员工好、、、", "image": null, "praise_count": 372, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132184}, {"id": 239135, "content": "一干正事就都不靠谱 过来拿吃拿喝的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858602}, {"id": 239391, "content": "“我刚工作那会儿，就没节假日这个概念...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967846}, {"id": 238881, "content": "主要是有关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664489}, {"id": 238882, "content": "这个工作可简单了，随便做就是", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673280}, {"id": 238886, "content": "还没上班，来看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776144}, {"id": 238888, "content": "每季度or每年必来的廉洁，反腐败培训", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726756}, {"id": 238889, "content": "“一点都不懂事，来那么早都不知道把经理的茶泡一下？！”对不起，我是策划，不是行政，作为我的主管你喜欢溜须拍马自降身份是你的事，不要拉上我", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134926}, {"id": 238890, "content": "天天发些狼性文化，或者马云刘强东的名言，其实压根人家都没说过这些话", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667615}, {"id": 238893, "content": "都是创业者，我们之间客气啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143773}, {"id": 238894, "content": "“年轻人就是来吃苦的”，如果自身出发，努力吃苦上进还行。如果是不熟的前辈，也不是某方面权威，就让我感觉被绑架，没有感觉到真诚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477451}, {"id": 239150, "content": "公司赚了钱你们才有钱赚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709643}, {"id": 238897, "content": "加油( ¯ᒡ̱¯ )و\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120477}, {"id": 238898, "content": "任何意见都是过来人的重要经验，你都该听着", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75801}, {"id": 238899, "content": "千万别得罪人，千万别出头。导致怕这怕那畏首畏尾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138516}, {"id": 238900, "content": "关注事情就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130777}, {"id": 238901, "content": "emmm…最近的话题学生党表示很懵啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039682}, {"id": 242229, "content": "不要和同事做朋友……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043232}, {"id": 238902, "content": "按规则办", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079787}, {"id": 238904, "content": "不要给我拍马屁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481321}, {"id": 238905, "content": "从基层做起好，要踏实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208955}, {"id": 238906, "content": "考的差，在哪都差。教你的也差，叉叉××", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209052}, {"id": 238907, "content": "不敢说 怕上级看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 238908, "content": "惊了，发言的人是认真的嘛？看眼色，合群，学好技术竟然是无用的建议？？！我真的好奇这些参加调查的人是哪些人了！包括出选项的小编！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890768}, {"id": 238910, "content": "要坐在客户的办公室里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014095}, {"id": 238911, "content": "保持和同事的距离感", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128744}, {"id": 238912, "content": "我觉得还可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137605}, {"id": 238913, "content": "有时候哈不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137605}, {"id": 238914, "content": "对讨厌的人也要脸上过得去 呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646202}, {"id": 243266, "content": "多忍忍就好了，后来有一天我忍不下去了，释放了自我的天性，然后…事情极其高效顺利", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993110}, {"id": 238915, "content": "学好数学能致富。金泽为你找出路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851995}, {"id": 238916, "content": "不着急，慢慢来，呵呵了，别人都上去了听你的？？？比你还差吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141762}, {"id": 241989, "content": "今天的培训会务必准时参加，手里活儿忙的话拿到会上去做……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539631}, {"id": 238918, "content": "由上至下，不要主动找领导给他压力（笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780915}, {"id": 238919, "content": "成功学神论，把自己变成别人想要看到的样子。。。于是就学废了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076260}, {"id": 238920, "content": "年轻人好好干，超盈不会亏待你的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008593}, {"id": 238921, "content": "只说虚的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086979}, {"id": 238924, "content": "年轻人，吃点儿小亏不要紧，眼光要放长远……", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 238925, "content": "你给公司创造什么。你才会得到什么。这是等价交换", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141431}, {"id": 241486, "content": "工作中要多给自己压力，努力做到最好，工资3k。幸好走了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152929}, {"id": 238928, "content": "最近都是职场啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}]}